Mike, Mark and Thomas Thurman             (A Medi‘val Graphical Adventure Game)

    Welcome  to  the game. If INSTALL.EXE didn't come with this archive, here's
how to unpack the program so that you can begin playing:

          i) Create a new directory to put Avalot into. (e.g. `MD \AVALOT')
         ii) Move into that directory. (e.g. `CD \AVALOT')
        iii) Run this program again from there, and press `Y'.

    ONLY  if  you  are  at  stage  three  now,  press  `Y'  to start unpacking.
Otherwise, press `N' now, and go through the steps above.

    Good luck in the game!                                     Unpack?я
